Package sg.dex.starfish

Interface Bundle

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Asset
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MemoryBundle, RemoteBundle
    public interface Bundle
extends Asset
    Interface representing an immutable asset bundle. The sub-asset belongs to the bundle are defined in the asset metadata contents.The contents of the bundle can be other named asset
    Version:
    0.5
    Author:
    Mike
